premise_source_doc_sentence: Sarah Louise Palin  (  -LSB- ˈpeɪlᵻn -RSB- née Heath ; born February 11 , 1964  )  is an American politician , commentator , and author who served as the ninth Governor of Alaska from 2006 until her resignation in 2009 .
Sarah Palin  (  born 1964  )  , former governor of Alaska and 2008 U.S. Republican vice-presidential nominee
